## Warm Up

Warm Up:run 1/4 mile or bike 2 miles or row 250m followed by: 3 rounds of 10 air squats, 10 double unders, 10 jumping jacks,   10 pull ups.

## WOD

WOD 51

### Étudiant

50 burpees for time.

### Avancée

75 burpees for time.

### Traceur

100 burpees for time.

